BTC tracker dashboard.

Local run:
- Open `/Users/mjamiv/coding/btc-chart/btc_tracker/index.html` in a browser.

Automations:
- Daily historical BTC prices are refreshed by `/Users/mjamiv/coding/btc-chart/btc_tracker/.github/workflows/update-historical-prices.yml`.
- Security scans run in `/Users/mjamiv/coding/btc-chart/btc_tracker/.github/workflows/security-sweep.yml`.

Security note:
- GitHub Pages is public-by-design for static assets. See `/Users/mjamiv/coding/btc-chart/btc_tracker/SECURITY.md` before redeploying sensitive data.
